#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:8
msgid "AGENTS.md の次に、翻訳作業を Skills 化してみる"
msgstr "After AGENTS.md, I tried turning translation work into a Skill"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:11
msgid "はじめに"
msgstr "Introduction"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:13
msgid "前回、Sphinx + ablog で作っている個人技術ノートに ``AGENTS.md`` を導入した。"
msgstr ""
"Previously, I introduced ``AGENTS.md`` into my personal technical blog built"
" with Sphinx + ablog."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:15
msgid "その後、英語ページ向けの ``.po`` 翻訳を進める中で、 翻訳作業には毎回同じ確認や判断が多いことに気づいた。"
msgstr ""
"Later, as I continued translating ``.po`` for English pages, I realized that"
" many of the same checks and decisions were made each time I translated."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:18
msgid "今回は、その翻訳まわりの作業を Codex Skills として切り出してみた記録である。"
msgstr ""
"This post records my attempt to separate that translation workflow into a "
"Codex Skill."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:21
msgid "なぜ翻訳作業を Skills 化するのか"
msgstr "Why turn translation work into a Skill?"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:23
msgid "翻訳作業では、単に日本語を英語に置き換えるだけでは済まない。"
msgstr ""
"Translation work involves more than simply replacing Japanese with English."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:25
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:96
msgid "``msgid`` は変更しない"
msgstr "Do not change ``msgid``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:26
msgid "空の ``msgstr`` だけを埋める"
msgstr "Fill only empty ``msgstr``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:27
msgid "既存翻訳を不用意に上書きしない"
msgstr "Do not carelessly overwrite existing translations"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:28
msgid "reStructuredText の記法を壊さない"
msgstr "Do not break reStructuredText notation"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:29
msgid "``rye run doit doc`` でビルド確認する"
msgstr "Check the build with ``rye run doit doc``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:30
msgid "Sphinx の ``<translated>`` 警告を見て ``.po`` を直す"
msgstr "Check Sphinx ``<translated>`` warnings and fix the relevant ``.po`` entries"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:31
msgid "英語として自然な技術ブログ文体にする"
msgstr "Use natural English technical-blog prose"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:33
msgid "これらを毎回 Codex に説明するのは手間がかかる。"
msgstr "It takes time to explain these to Codex every time."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:35
msgid "また、同じ説明を繰り返すことは、 会話のトークン消費も増やしてしまう。"
msgstr ""
"Repeating the same explanation also increases token usage in the "
"conversation."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:38
msgid "そこで、翻訳作業専用の手順として Skills にまとめることにした。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, I decided to organize them into Skills as procedures dedicated to"
" translation work."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:41
msgid "AGENTS.md と Skills の役割分担"
msgstr "Dividing responsibilities between AGENTS.md and Skills"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:43
msgid "今回の整理では、``AGENTS.md`` と Skills を次のように分けて考えた。"
msgstr ""
"In this organization, we separated ``AGENTS.md`` and Skills as follows."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:45
msgid "``AGENTS.md`` には、リポジトリ全体のルールを書く。"
msgstr "Use ``AGENTS.md`` for repository-wide rules."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:47
msgid "日本語で説明する"
msgstr "Explain things in Japanese"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:48
msgid "Rye を使う"
msgstr "Use Rye"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:49
msgid "生成物を直接編集しない"
msgstr "Do not edit generated files directly"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:50
msgid "記事本文は日本語を正とする"
msgstr "Treat the Japanese article body as the source of truth"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:51
msgid "英語ページは翻訳版として扱う"
msgstr "Treat English pages as translated versions"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:53
msgid "一方で、Skills には特定作業の手順を書く。"
msgstr "Use Skills for procedures tied to specific tasks."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:55
msgid ""
"今回作った ``sphinx-ablog-translation`` Skill では、 gettext / sphinx-intl の ``.po``"
" 翻訳作業に必要な判断や確認をまとめた。"
msgstr ""
"The ``sphinx-ablog-translation`` Skill I created this time summarizes the "
"judgments and confirmations necessary for gettext / sphinx-intl ``.po`` "
"translation work."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:59
msgid "作成した Skill"
msgstr "The Skill I created"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:61
msgid "今回作成した Skill は次の場所に置いた。"
msgstr "I placed the Skill I created this time in the following location."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:67
msgid "Codex の個人設定配下に置くことで、 このPC上の Codex から利用できるようにする意図である。"
msgstr ""
"By placing it under Codex's personal settings, it is intended to be "
"available from Codex on this PC."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:70
msgid "リポジトリ配下に置くのではなく、 個人プロファイル側に置くことで、 同じ種類の翻訳作業を他のリポジトリでも使い回しやすくなる。"
msgstr ""
"By placing it in your personal profile rather than under the repository, it "
"becomes easier to reuse the same type of translation work in other "
"repositories."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:75
msgid "Skill に含めたもの"
msgstr "What I included in the Skill"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:77
msgid "最初から翻訳を完全自動化するのではなく、 まずは検査と作業方針を中心にした。"
msgstr ""
"Rather than completely automating translation from the beginning, we started"
" by focusing on inspection and work policies."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:80
msgid "構成は次のようにした。"
msgstr "The configuration was as follows."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:93
msgid "``SKILL.md`` には、翻訳時の基本ルールを書いた。"
msgstr "In ``SKILL.md``, I wrote the basic rules for translation."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:95
msgid "日本語 ``.rst`` を正とする"
msgstr "Treat the Japanese ``.rst`` as the source of truth"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:97
msgid "``msgstr`` を埋める"
msgstr "Fill in ``msgstr``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:98
msgid "コマンド、パス、設定名、コード片は保持する"
msgstr "Retain commands, paths, configuration names, and code fragments"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:99
msgid "翻訳後に ``rye run doit doc`` を実行する"
msgstr "Run ``rye run doit doc`` after translation"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:100
msgid "ビルド警告があれば ``.po`` の該当箇所を修正する"
msgstr "If there is a build warning, fix the corresponding entry in the ``.po`` file"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:102
msgid "``style-guide.md`` には、 直訳ではなく自然な英語にするための方針を書いた。"
msgstr ""
"In ``style-guide.md``, I wrote a policy for creating natural English rather "
"than literal translations."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:105
msgid "``glossary.md`` には、 この技術ノートでよく出る用語の訳語を置いた。"
msgstr ""
"``glossary.md`` contains translations of terms that often appear in this "
"technical note."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:109
msgid "``po_status.py`` で未翻訳を確認する"
msgstr "Check untranslated entries with ``po_status.py``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:111
msgid ""
"``po_status.py`` は、``docs/locale/en`` 配下の ``.po`` を確認し、 次の情報を出すためのスクリプトである。"
msgstr ""
"``po_status.py`` is a script that checks ``.po`` under ``docs/locale/en`` "
"and outputs the following information."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:114
msgid "構文エラー"
msgstr "syntax error"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:115
msgid "空の ``msgstr``"
msgstr "empty ``msgstr``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:116
msgid "fuzzy"
msgstr "fuzzy"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:117
msgid "翻訳済み件数"
msgstr "number of translated entries"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:119
msgid "今回の確認では、次のような状態まで持っていけた。"
msgstr "In this check, I was able to reach the following state."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:127
msgid "この確認をスクリプトにしたことで、 毎回 Codex に集計用の Python を書かせる必要がなくなる。"
msgstr ""
"By making this check a script, there is no need to have Codex write Python "
"for aggregation each time."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:131
msgid "``check_po.py`` で rst 記法の崩れを検出する"
msgstr "Detect broken rst markup with ``check_po.py``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:133
msgid "翻訳作業で特に問題になったのは、 reStructuredText の記法が翻訳によって壊れることだった。"
msgstr ""
"A particular problem during the translation process was that the "
"reStructuredText notation was broken by translation."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:136
msgid "たとえば、次のような記法である。"
msgstr "For example, these forms are easy to break."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:138
msgid "インラインリテラルの ````...````"
msgstr "Inline literals written with double backticks"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:139
msgid "強調の ``**...**``"
msgstr "Emphasis ``**...**``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:140
msgid "脚注参照の ``[#task]_``"
msgstr "``[#task]_`` in footnote reference"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:141
msgid "リンク参照の ```name`_``"
msgstr "```name`_`` of link reference"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:142
msgid "ロールの ``:doc:`...``` や ``:kbd:`...```"
msgstr "``:doc:`...```` and ``:kbd:`...```` in roles"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:144
msgid ""
"機械翻訳を通すと、引用符やバッククォートが片側だけ変わることがある。 その結果、Sphinx のビルド時に ``<translated>`` "
"警告が出る。"
msgstr ""
"When passed through machine translation, quotation marks and backticks may "
"change on only one side. As a result, you will receive a ``<translated>`` "
"warning when building Sphinx."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:147
msgid "そこで ``check_po.py`` では、 翻訳後の ``msgstr`` に対して、 壊れやすい記法を検査するようにした。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, ``check_po.py`` checks the translated ``msgstr`` for fragile "
"notations."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:152
msgid "実際に使ってみた結果"
msgstr "Results of actual use"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:154
msgid "Skill を作る過程で、既存の英訳 ``.po`` にもいくつか問題が見つかった。"
msgstr ""
"In the process of creating the Skill, we found some problems with the "
"existing English translation ``.po``."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:156
msgid "``msgstr`` 内の余分な引用符"
msgstr "Extra quotes in ``msgstr``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:157
msgid "````...```` の閉じ忘れ"
msgstr "Forgetting to close an inline literal"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:158
msgid "URL付きリンクの消失"
msgstr "Loss of links with URLs"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:159
msgid "脚注・参照名の不一致"
msgstr "Mismatched footnote/reference name"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:161
msgid "これらを直したうえで、最終的に次の確認が通った。"
msgstr ""
"After correcting these, the following confirmation was finally passed."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:170
msgid "さらに、``rye run doit doc`` も ja/en ともに成功した。"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, ``rye run doit doc`` was also successful for both ja and en."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:173
msgid "Skills 化してよかったこと"
msgstr "What worked well after turning it into a Skill"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:175
msgid "今回の作業で、Skills は「手順書」と「小さな道具箱」の中間のように使えると感じた。"
msgstr ""
"During this work, I felt that Skills could be used as something between a "
"procedure manual and a small toolbox."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:177
msgid "特によかったのは次の点である。"
msgstr "The following points were particularly good."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:179
msgid "毎回説明していた翻訳ルールを短く呼び出せる"
msgstr ""
"You can quickly recall the translation rules that were explained each time."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:180
msgid "集計や検査の Python を毎回生成しなくてよい"
msgstr "No need to generate Python for aggregation or inspection every time"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:181
msgid "トークン消費を減らしやすい"
msgstr "Easy to reduce token consumption"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:182
msgid "翻訳作業で壊れやすいポイントを蓄積できる"
msgstr "You can accumulate fragile points through translation work."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:183
msgid "AGENTS.md を肥大化させずに済む"
msgstr "No need to enlarge AGENTS.md"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:185
msgid "AGENTS.md はリポジトリ全体の基本方針、 Skills は特定作業の手順と道具、 という分担が見えてきた。"
msgstr ""
"We can now see a division between AGENTS.md, the basic policy for the entire"
" repository, and Skills, procedures and tools for specific tasks."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:190
msgid "まだ課題もある"
msgstr "There are still challenges"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:192
msgid "一方で、翻訳そのものを完全に自動化するのはまだ慎重にしたい。"
msgstr ""
"On the other hand, I still want to be cautious about completely automating "
"the translation itself."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:194
msgid "機械翻訳で ``msgstr`` を一括で埋めることはできるが、 自然な英語になっているか、 技術的に意味がずれていないかは別問題である。"
msgstr ""
"It is possible to fill in ``msgstr`` all at once with machine translation, "
"but whether it is natural English or whether the meaning is technically "
"correct is another matter."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:198
msgid "そのため、今回の Skill では、 まず検査と作業方針を中心にした。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, in this Skill, we first focused on inspection and work policy."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:201
msgid ""
"翻訳自動化スクリプトを入れるとしても、 既存翻訳を上書きしない、 空の ``msgstr`` だけを対象にする、 ビルド警告を必ず確認する、 "
"といった制約が必要だと感じた。"
msgstr ""
"Even if I were to include a translation automation script, I felt that "
"restrictions were necessary, such as not overwriting existing translations, "
"targeting only empty ``msgstr``, and always checking for build warnings."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:208
msgid "今後の展望"
msgstr "Future plans"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:210
msgid "今後は、この Skill を実際の翻訳作業で使いながら育てていきたい。"
msgstr ""
"In the future, I would like to develop this skill by using it in actual "
"translation work."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:212
msgid "追加したい候補としては、次のようなものがある。"
msgstr "Suggestions for additions include the following:"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:214
msgid "空の ``msgstr`` だけを翻訳する補助スクリプト"
msgstr "Auxiliary script that only translates empty ``msgstr``"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:215
msgid "Sphinx の警告ログから該当 ``.po`` を逆引きするスクリプト"
msgstr ""
"A script that reverse looks up the corresponding ``.po`` from the Sphinx "
"warning log."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:216
msgid "よくある翻訳崩れの自動修正"
msgstr "Automatic correction of common translation errors"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:217
msgid "技術ノート用語集の拡充"
msgstr "Expansion of technical note glossary"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:218
msgid "重要記事だけ人手で英語を磨く運用"
msgstr "A workflow for manually polishing only important articles"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:220
msgid "まずは、未翻訳確認と rst 記法チェックを安定して使うところから始める。"
msgstr ""
"First, start by using the untranslated confirmation and rst syntax check in "
"a stable manner."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:223
msgid "おわりに"
msgstr "Closing"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:225
msgid "AGENTS.md を導入したことで、リポジトリ全体の作業方針を Codex に伝えやすくなった。"
msgstr ""
"With the introduction of AGENTS.md, it has become easier to communicate the "
"working policy of the entire repository to Codex."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:227
msgid "さらに今回、翻訳作業を Skills 化したことで、 特定作業の手順や検査を再利用しやすくなった。"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, by converting translation work into skills, it has become "
"easier to reuse procedures and inspections for specific tasks."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:230
msgid ""
"個人技術ノートのように、記事作成、翻訳、ビルド、公開が少しずつ絡み合うリポジトリでは、 こうした小さな Skill を育てていくことが、 "
"作業の安定化と省力化につながりそうである。"
msgstr ""
"In repositories like personal technical notes, where article creation, "
"translation, build, and publication are intertwined little by little, "
"developing these small skills is likely to lead to more stable work and "
"labor savings."
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst:235
msgid "記事情報"
msgstr "Article information"
#: ../../../blog/posts/2026-05-11-sphinx-ablog-translation-skill.rst
msgid "著者"
msgstr "author"
